articles.author: Joe Cash
articles.title: China's exports rise solidly, but slower imports temper outlook - Reuters
articles.description: China's exports grew more quickly and for a second month in May, suggesting factory owners are managing to find buyers overseas and providing some relief to the economy as it battles to mount a durable recovery.
